Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是基于大量调查与验证而制作的虚构作品
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本动画以发生了大地震的首都圈为假想舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.98,0:00:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在动画中 会有部分与实际相出入的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.98,0:00:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原作为追求逼真效果 经过了充分的模拟测试
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.58,0:01:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天尽是些烦心事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.43,0:01:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆 让这种世界毁灭掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.14,0:01:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地震?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.60,0:02:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 我去下厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.63,0:02:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:56.01,title1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,660)\fad(300,0)}「毁灭、世界」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗 坚持住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻点轻点  小心地上凹凸不平
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「每天尽是些烦心事 干脆 让这种世界毁灭掉吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.12,0:04:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻站着找死啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.50,0:04:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠…悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.17,0:04:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…你们有看见过小男孩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定 还在洗手间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.33,0:05:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.71,0:05:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.24,0:05:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面就是出口 慢慢走不要慌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你 快回来 那边危险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.84,0:05:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的女孩 快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你 那边危险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.12,0:06:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为刚才的地震 那边已经起火了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去西面避难
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 可…可是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.15,0:06:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是地震
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.14,0:06:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真危险 简直是千钧一发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.10,0:06:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…刚才那位?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.07,0:06:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能站起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.51,0:07:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人吗 刚才的小弟弟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.53,0:07:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我让他一个人去洗手间了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.94,0:07:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.15,0:07:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和弟弟两个人来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.03,0:07:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去找他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.53,0:07:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个好姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.74,0:07:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗手间…我让他一个人去洗手间了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.98,0:07:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是没人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.12,0:07:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.76,0:07:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.91,0:07:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来找弟弟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.48,0:08:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.58,0:08:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.91,0:08:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.28,0:08:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.53,0:08:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这么大的地震
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.29,0:08:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.06,0:08:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 你们看到过小男孩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七八岁左右的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩倒是看到过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过都是和父母在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.61,0:08:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 没帮上你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 你们看到过小男孩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.59,0:08:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长这么高 七八岁左右
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.61,0:09:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…穿的是黄绿色的T恤 胸前有条横线
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.37,0:09:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 没注意过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.90,0:09:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一楼玩具柜台那边倒看见过几个没人管的男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.11,0:09:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.81,0:09:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.65,0:09:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找别的楼梯下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这儿很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.66,0:09:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.13,0:10:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.07,0:10:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好 小姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.20,0:10:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你别这样乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道那有多危险吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.06,0:10:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是悠贵在玩具柜…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.09,0:10:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 但是连你也受伤了那还有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.84,0:10:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.74,0:10:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵有没有受伤你怎么知道!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.20,0:10:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 那边危险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.89,0:11:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.08,0:11:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 是我说错了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.49,0:11:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟他没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.31,0:11:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.49,0:11:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起来找 所以不要乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.44,0:11:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.43,0:11:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 一二三
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.13,0:11:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.62,0:12:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 大家有受伤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 这里很危险 你们都去避难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.66,0:12:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我们在找一个男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.51,0:12:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿这黄绿色衣服的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.07,0:12:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经差不多找了一遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最后一个小孩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.31,0:12:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的孩子 恐怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.25,0:12:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵 你在哪里啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.17,0:12:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答啊 悠贵!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵!悠贵!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 我们先出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.36,0:13:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁还没有卷入烟尘时…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.99,0:13:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 要走的话你走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.36,0:13:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能扔下悠贵不管
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.29,0:13:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你好好想想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.01,0:13:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么样才能活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.16,0:13:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果悠贵还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.87,0:13:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定已经在避难了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.59,0:13:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你不能死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.99,0:13:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要活着找到悠贵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.49,0:13:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「啊 顺便去买点饮料吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.02,0:13:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饮料! 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.53,0:13:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我在这里找一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.27,0:14:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.31,0:14:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有谁在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.94,0:14:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊 我在这里 救命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这就去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是姐姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.24,0:14:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵 受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.74,0:14:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.25,0:14:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着哦 马上救你出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.28,0:14:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撑起那边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.38,0:14:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.73,0:14:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.27,0:14:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}谢谢您 不用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事太好了 真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.35,0:14:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.90,0:15:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.68,0:15:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要等雨停吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.33,0:15:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里很危险 换个地方把
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火灾?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.59,0:15:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.63,0:15:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.07,0:15:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这里可以避避雨了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.15,0:15:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}没事太好了 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.59,0:16:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不通吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这边也打不通
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是信号基站遭殃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.45,0:16:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复一遍 大约4小时前 15时46分左右
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.83,0:16:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关东地区发生了大地震
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.55,0:16:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次地震的震源地位于东京湾北部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.89,0:16:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,震源深度约为25公里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.03,0:16:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推测里氏震级为8.0
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.41,0:16:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8级地震?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.04,0:16:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}请大家注意余震以及海啸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 看这边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.17,0:16:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}受到此次地震的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.28,0:16:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手机能用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}所有的交通设施都暂停运作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.63,0:16:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东京消防属称
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.72,0:16:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都内各地发生大规模的火灾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.88,0:16:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}请居民们尽快避难
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和妈妈没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家住哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砧公园的附近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.48,0:16:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 成城那里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.11,0:16:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家在三轩茶屋那里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.73,0:16:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全打不通
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似只能接受地面电视波段了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs38}地面电视波段是利用日本微波数字广播电视\N“ISDB-T（integrated service digital broadcasting-terrestrial）”向便携设备发送广播电视的服务的名称
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.90,0:17:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们再看看情况吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.39,0:17:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会帮你们一起想回家的方法的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.31,0:17:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要对我们那么亲切呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢 做为人应该的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你姐姐 刚才非常拼命的找你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.07,0:17:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个好姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢谢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快点回去 把那个送给妈妈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.88,0:17:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 还没问过你们名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.44,0:17:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫日下部 真理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫悠贵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是小野泽 未来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫未来啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.61,0:17:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个好名字哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.64,0:17:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这名字我不大喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:18:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢哦 姐姐的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.60,0:18:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中学生?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.94,0:18:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中学一年级
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.67,0:18:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠贵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.88,0:18:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小学三年级
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.61,0:18:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个一起出门 真要好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般般
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.01,0:18:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情变成这样子 都怪那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈总是只顾着工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.29,0:18:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们两个自己去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.74,0:18:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着真难受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.96,0:18:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家 是我和我妈妈还有女儿三人家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也总是因工作 照顾不了女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.29,0:18:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我女儿很喜欢荡秋千
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想努力工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬到一栋可以装秋千的房子里去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.78,0:18:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是慢慢拖着的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.99,0:18:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说不定就过了喜欢荡秋千的年龄了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.43,0:18:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我去拿点行李哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.41,0:18:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的摩托车停在这附近的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.82,0:19:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人 说不定不会回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.63,0:19:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 她没回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.60,0:19:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她没有义务照顾我们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.02,0:19:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是余震
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.53,0:19:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大地震之后 总会有几次这样的余震
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.59,0:19:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的算是小的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.72,0:19:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里应该没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.76,0:19:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 你们两个肚子饿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.88,0:20:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这里有蛋糕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道还在吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.95,0:20:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快乐 雛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.13,0:20:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 今天是我女儿的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.67,0:20:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就4岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫小雛?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.25,0:20:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 给
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.30,0:20:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.48,0:20:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过外表已经烂了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 生日蛋糕还是圆的好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.46,0:20:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.07,0:20:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后我们该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.28,0:20:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.70,0:20:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之现在先休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.26,0:20:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天一定也会很忙碌的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.60,0:22:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跨海天桥崩塌 多人受伤
